title: 7 Cuyahoga County cities unite to ask voters to curb deer population: Best of the Beat
text:
7 Cuyahoga County cities unite to ask voters to curb deer population: Best of the Beat 
Published By: Cleveland.com - Today 
Seven southwestern Cuyahoga County cities hope to implement a regional plan to curb deer population, mayors from the municipalities said....
